  • Souvenir d'André Geerts

Souvenir d'André Geerts

  • Par Liliane Schraûwen
  • Le 24/12/2012
  • Commentaires (41528)
  • Dans Bande dessinée

​La mort, une fois de plus.

Normal. Il est un âge, forcément, où quelquefois on l'a croisée. Celle des aînés, celle des proches qui nous précèdent sur le chemin, et certains laissent un tel vide, la peine est si grande, que le temps n'y fait rien. Celle d'amis. Celle d'êtres plus jeunes, très jeunes parfois. Celle d'artistes dont l'œuvre nous a touchés, et l'on a l'impression de les connaître mieux que nombre de ces gens que l'on côtoie chaque jour. Leur œuvre du moins leur survit et l'on continue de s'y perdre et de l'aimer, l'on continue de s'y reconnaître.

La tienne aujourd'hui, André. Artiste, certes, qui continuera de vivre dans Jojo, Mamy, Marie, Violaine, Gros-Louis… Mais pas seulement. Car j'ai un peu – très peu – connu l'homme aussi. Rencontres au hasard de Salons du Livre, lors d'expositions, chez des amis communs… Il nous est arrivé de dîner à la même table, de partager un verre. Nous discutions littérature, cinéma, bande dessinée évidemment. Je me souviens, tu parlais de ton enfance. Tu m'as raconté ton bref passage au Collège Saint-Pierre d'Uccle où justement j'enseignais à cette époque, dont l'ancien directeur t'a servi de modèle pour le fameux "Monsieur le Directeur" de Jojo. La grille devant l'entrée, le bureau du proviseur et l'attente tremblante, devant sa porte, du contrevenant aux innombrables règles imposées aux potaches dont tu as brièvement fait partie. Le petit escalier descendant vers la cour de récréation que l'on retrouve dans Jojo au pensionnat, celui-là même que si souvent j'ai emprunté pour aller prendre mon rang dans cette cour, et sur les marches duquel je me suis un jour trouvée quasiment assommée par un ballon de foot mal – ou trop bien – dirigé.

Parfois nous nous croisions par hasard, en rue, en ville. Tu m'embrassais, nous bavardions quelques instants. Salut, que deviens-tu? Qu'est-ce que tu fais de beau pour le moment? À un de ces jours… Prochain hasard, prochaine rencontre.

Plus jamais.

Un jour, tu m'as avoué avoir seulement feuilleté mes livres, les avoir parcourus, mais sans les lire vraiment. "Trop noir, disais-tu, trop triste… J'aurais du mal à le supporter, je crois…"

Car sous ton sourire tendre et derrière ton rire, il t'arrivait d'être triste. Quelques-uns le savaient. Et fragile. Avec ce côté rêveur qui, sans doute, t'a permis de si bien recréer le monde de l'enfance. Boule, Cédric, sont mignons et drôles, certes. Mais Jojo est… vrai. Ce n'est pas un stéréotype, ce n'est pas une figure de papier. Il fait sourire, mais jamais il ne fait rire. Il n'est pas ce gagman en culotte courte vivant dans une famille comme il n'en existe plus guère, entre des parents presque caricaturaux à force d'être idéaux, avec un chien, une tortue, un grand-père à la Cauvin.

Jojo est vivant. C'est un vrai petit garçon, tendre, malicieux, vulnérable, coléreux parfois, injuste à l'occasion, impulsif, mais rempli d'amour et, surtout, dans une énorme demande d'affection, de protection, d'amitié. Attachant et généreux. Comme toi sans doute. Fondamentalement "gentil", totalement craquant. Comme toi encore.

Je t'ai connu… mon Dieu, ça fait longtemps. Tu avais le cheveu noir et bouclé. Je t'ai connu le crâne rasé. Puis bouclé toujours, mais avec plus de blanc que de noir dans tes mèches folles. Je me souviens de ta maison où je suis venue un jour, qui te ressemblait. Je me souviens de ton sourire. De ton regard un peu flou dont le strabisme léger a dû t'inspirer On opère Gros-Louis.

Et puis, hier soir, ces quelques mots pendant le journal télévisé : "André Geerts nous a quittés. Il avait 54 ans. Jojo est orphelin". Tristesse. Incrédulité. Ce n'est pas possible. Pas lui. Ce doit être une erreur. Il est trop jeune…

Tu aimais le tennis, le vélo, la moto. Tu te refusais à posséder et même à conduire une voiture. Tu aimais l'amitié, les rencontres, le vin. Tu étais vivant. Avec des projets, avec des tas de choses à faire encore, à découvrir, à créer. Avec des Jojo à inventer, des Mademoiselle Louise à incarner…

Que s'est-il passé, dis-moi? C'est quoi, cette "mort brutale" et cette "longue maladie" dont parlent les journaux ce matin? C'est quoi ce crabe qui a eu raison de toi? La tristesse a donc gagné, pour de bon…

Tu nous as quittés, tu es parti. C'est comme ça qu'on dit quand on ne veut pas utiliser le terme de "mort". J'aimerais croire que, en effet, tu es "parti". Seulement parti. Pour où? J'aimerais t'imaginer entrant dans les pages de tes albums, intégrant pour de vrai l'univers tendre et naïf de tes personnages. J'aimerais me dire qu'il existe un ailleurs, un quelque part où tu as retrouvé tes copains d'enfance et l'affection protectrice d'une mamy au grand cœur. J'aimerais croire que tu t'en es allé dans les nuages, sur ton vélo ou à moto, et que tu poursuis ton chemin, là-bas, de l'autre côté du ciel, de l'autre côté du soleil. De l'autre côté de la vie.

J'aimerais…

Mais je peux te dire qu'ici, le bleu du ciel et le vert des prairies sont devenus bien ternes. Il n'y a pas que Jojo qui soit orphelin. Son chagrin aujourd'hui doit être tel qu'aucun câlin de Mamy ne pourra le consoler, jamais. Nous sommes tous orphelins avec lui.

Et malheureux, tellement malheureux.

Mercredi 28 juillet 2010

The most exciting new trains coming in 2025
промокод рив гош на повторный заказ
Amazing adventures, extraordinary landscapes and fabulous cuisine — the world’s greatest railway journeys are an unforgettable experience that can immerse you in the culture of a new country.

Demand for luxury “land cruise” trains with five-star hotel-style accommodation is booming. 2025 will see several new trains take to the rails for the first time, offering new opportunities to explore Italy, France, Saudi Arabia and the United Kingdom.

But the best railway journeys don’t have to be the most expensive. There’s an ever-evolving world of train trips out there. Here are some of the key developments in the coming year
Two of Europe’s great capitals are now linked by their first direct high-speed train connection. Germany’s Deutsche Bahn introduced a daytime InterCity Express (ICE) service between Paris and Berlin on December 16 and is planning to add a second route between the two capitals in 2026.

Taking advantage of its new fleet of 200 mph (322 kph) ICE3neo trains, the once-a-day service takes around eight hours in each direction, also serving Strasbourg, Karlsruhe and Frankfurt on its 546-mile (878-kilometer) journey.

Fares start from around $60, and each train has capacity for 444 passengers, of which 111 can enjoy the additional comfort of leather seats and at-seat refreshments in first class.

The new high-speed ICE service is the first direct daytime train between Paris and Berlin since the 1990s and complements the Nightjet sleeper service introduced in 2023.

It may not be as fast as flying — some of the journey has to use lower speed “classic” lines to bridge gaps in the European high-speed network — but it is undoubtedly a more sustainable and more stylish way to travel across Europe.

<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Owning an luxury bag has long been synonymous with prestige, fashion, and elegance. From the legendary quilted Chanel to the timeless Hermès Birkin, these bags have the ability to elevate any look and showcase your personal style. But the high costs frequently make them seem unattainable for most style enthusiasts.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">What if we said to you it’s feasible to possess the luxury handbag of your desires without overspending? With the right insight, approaches, and a discerning eye, you can make that dream into reality. This article delves deep into how you can score luxury bags for cheaper, offering tips on finding genuine offers, considering options, and taking wise investment choices.</p>

<h2 class="font-bold text-h3 leading-<>0px] pt-<>1px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Why Luxury Bags Are Truly A Great Investment Owning</h2>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Before we jump into ways to snag designer bags for less, it’s crucial to realize the reason they are deserve the price in the first place.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">1. Timeless Looks</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">High-end handbags rarely go out of fashion. A quality premium bag can be used for decades without losing its charm or trendiness. These pieces typically feature classic looks that endure fleeting fads, turning them wardrobe must-haves.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Next, Impeccable Quality</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Luxury labels like L. Vuitton, Gucci Co., and Prada Co. emphasize quality. Their bags are crafted using top-notch fabrics and precise techniques, delivering durability and lasting value. You’re more than purchasing a handbag—you’re investing in artistry.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">3. Impressive Resale Price</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">In contrast to throwaway style pieces, designer handbags often retain their worth over years. Some even increase in value, positioning them smart financial pieces. For illustration, the H. Birkin has been demonstrated to exceed the stock market on several instances.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Finally, Confidence Enhancer</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">There’s something unquestionably motivating about using a designer bag. It’s not just about looks; it’s about the lifestyle it stands for—personal success, achievement, and a appreciation for the higher-end choices in living.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">With that said, now that we’ve covered what makes high-end handbags are justify the attention, here’s how to get them for less.</p>

<h2 class="font-bold text-h3 leading-<>0px] pt-<>1px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Steps to for Score Designer Bags for Less.</h2>
<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">A best ways that lets you get one luxury bag minus the hefty cost tag is by buy second-hand. Resources including The RealReal, Fashion Phile, plus Vestiaire Collective specialize on used designer products, offering verified bags priced at a part of their full-price value.</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">When buying second-hand, here are a few things that you should bear mind:</p>

<ul class="pt-<>px] pb-<>px] pl-<>4px] list-disc <>amp;_ul]:pt-<>px] pt-<>px]">
<li class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] my-<>px] <>amp;>ol]:!pt-0 <>amp;>ol]:!pb-0 <>amp;>ul]:!pt-0 <>amp;>ul]:!pb-0" value="1">Confirm on authenticity: Always get through reliable brands who promise 100% authentic items. <li class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] my-<>px] <>amp;>ol]:!pt-0 <>amp;>ol]:!pb-0 <>amp;>ul]:!pt-0 <>amp;>ul]:!pb-0" value="2">Check a condition: Used may not always mean flawless. Check for a damage details or images shared.</li>
<li class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] my-<>px] <>amp;>ol]:!pt-0 <>amp;>ol]:!pb-0 <>amp;>ul]:!pt-0 <>amp;>ul]:!pb-0" value="3">Browse Prices: Look through different platforms to ensure you’ll be securing a most competitive deal.</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">2. Explore Discount Shops</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Many luxury labels have discount locations that companies offer big discounts on previous or overstocked goods. <p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Expert Hint: Keep in mind, not each factory products are created the same. <p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Owning an luxury handbag has always been synonymous with status, style, and elegance. From the iconic quilted Chanel to the timeless Hermès Birkin, these bags have the power to elevate any look and showcase your personal aesthetic. But the high costs frequently make them seem unattainable for most style enthusiasts.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">What if we told you it’s possible to possess the luxury handbag of your desires without overspending? With the right insight, approaches, and a keen eye, you can make that wish into actuality. This article delves thoroughly into how you can score luxury bags for cheaper, offering tips on discovering genuine offers, considering alternatives, and making wise investment decisions.</p>

<h2 class="font-bold text-h3 leading-<>0px] pt-<>1px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Reasons Luxury Handbags Are Truly Worth It</h2>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Before we dive into ways to get high-end bags for a bargain, it’s crucial to realize why they are worth the cost in the first place.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">1. Everlasting Styles</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Designer bags never go outdated style. A quality designer handbag can be used for a long time without sacrificing its beauty or relevance. These handbags usually include timeless looks that resist fleeting fads, making them wardrobe staples.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Second, Flawless Workmanship</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Luxury names like L. Vuitton, Gucci Co., and Prada emphasize excellence. Their products are designed using high-quality fabrics and precise techniques, delivering long-lasting quality and lasting value. You’re not just getting a bag—you’re acquiring mastery.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Third, Impressive Resale Profitability</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">In contrast to fast-fashion pieces, luxury purses usually maintain their price over time. Some actually gain in worth, turning them smart money items. For illustration, the H. Birkin has been shown to outperform the stock market on various cases.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Finally, Self-assurance Enhancer</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">There’s a quality unquestionably uplifting about using a designer handbag. It’s not just about looks; it’s about the value it represents—pride, accomplishment, and a appreciation for the finer things in life.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">At this point, now that we’ve covered what makes designer purses are worth the attention, here’s how to get hold of them for fewer costs.</p>

<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Owning an luxury bag has long been associated with prestige, fashion, and elegance. From the iconic stitched Chanel to the classic Hermès Birkin, these bags have the ability to elevate any outfit and showcase your individual aesthetic. But the high costs frequently make them seem out of reach for many style lovers.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">What if we said to you it’s possible to possess the luxury handbag of your desires without breaking the bank? With the proper insight, approaches, and a keen eye, you can make that wish into reality. This article delves thoroughly into how you can score luxury handbags for less, offering advice on discovering genuine deals, considering options, and taking wise financial choices.</p>

<h2 class="font-bold text-h3 leading-<>0px] pt-<>1px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Why Designer Bags Are A Great Investment Having</h2>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Before we step into how to get high-end bags for a bargain, it’s crucial to understand why they are worth the cost in the first place.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">To start with, Timeless Looks</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Designer purses rarely go out from style. A well-made luxury bag can be used for many years without diminishing its appeal or importance. These handbags typically include timeless styles that endure temporary fads, making them closet staples.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">2. Exquisite Quality</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Luxury brands like LV, Gucci Co., and P. focus on superiority. Their bags are made using premium resources and careful methods, guaranteeing durability and endurance. You’re not just purchasing a handbag—you’re investing in craft.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">3. Impressive Resale Profitability</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Differing from cheap fashion products, luxury bags often retain their price over the long term. Some in fact appreciate in price, turning them strong money items. For illustration, the Hermes Birkin has been proven to beat the stock market on multiple occasions.</p>

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">Finally, Self-assurance Enhancer</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">There’s something clearly motivating about owning a designer handbag. It’s beyond about appearance; it’s about what it represents—personal success, accomplishment, and a passion for the luxuries in life.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">With that said, now that we’ve covered what makes high-end purses are justify the attention, here’s how to get hold of them for fewer costs.</p>

<h2 class="font-bold text-h3 leading-<>0px] pt-<>1px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">The way on how to Score High-end Bags at Lower price.</h2>
<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">One of options to snag your high-end purse without a eye-watering cost point involves by purchase pre-owned. Resources including The RealReal, Fashionphile, and Vestiaire Collective deal in pre-loved designer goods, giving authentic handbags at a fraction from its original value.</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">When buying used, here is a few points you should bear thought:</p>

<ul class="pt-<>px] pb-<>px] pl-<>4px] list-disc <>amp;_ul]:pt-<>px] pt-<>px]">

<h3 class="font-bold text-h4 leading-<>0px] pt-<>5px] pb-<>px] <>amp;_a]:underline-offset-<>px] <>amp;_.underline]:underline-offset-<>px]" dir="ltr">two. Explore Discount Retailers</h3>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Many designer names run outlet stores in which companies provide substantial savings over past-season or overstocked items. <p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Insider Tip: Not all factory items are created equal. <p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">three. Hold off until Sales & Yearly Offers</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Designer bags do not go reduced frequently, but in cases where they do, this creates a golden chance to snag deals big.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">– Look at big department stores including Nordstrom, Saks Fifth Avenue, and Bloomingdale’s at their seasonal sales.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">– Stay alert to watch for brand-specific discounts around holidays or final season offers.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">four. Keep Up on E-commerce Stores</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Marketplaces like Farfetch, SSENSE, plus Net-a-Porter sometimes feature discounts for certain high-end items. <p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">Suggestion: Try discount-watching software like ShopTagr as well as Honey to monitor price drops on the exact bags you have watching.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">5. Rent Before Purchasing</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">When you’re unsure of committing on the spend for a high-end purse, think about renting a bag beforehand. That’s a great option to try different looks before making a buy.</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">6. Choose toward Wallet-Friendly Choices</p>
<p class="text-body font-regular leading-<>4px] pt-<>px] pb-<>px]" dir="ltr">If owning a high-end handbag fully won’t be in your financial reach, explore names who offer comparable quality along with style for a more budget-friendly cost.</p>
